@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api/notifications

### Test Notification (no auth)
POST {{baseUrl}}/test

### Notification Status (no auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/status

### Send Menu Notification (any authenticated)
POST {{baseUrl}}/send-menu
Authorization: Bearer {{ANY_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Today's Menu",
  "message": "Check out the delicious breakfast!",
  "url": "/"
}

### Send Menu Notification To All Students (admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/send-menu-all
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Today's Menu",
  "message": "Breakfast served at 8 AM"
}

### Admin: List Notifications
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}

### Admin: Unread Notifications
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/unread
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}

### Admin: Unread Count
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/count
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}

### Admin: Mark All Read
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/read-all
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}


